Shank's Take:
Oh, the bird? I was quite surprised to see one of them out in Faylil. I respect the attempt to break out of one's traditions. Rebelling against the status quo takes bravery. That is what I would say if you didn't immediately join a team of fools hell-bent on stopping us from changing the status quo. Sigh...

Dagger's Take:
That bird frustrates me. Seeing it take flight just reminds me how small my wings are. WHO NEEDS THE AIR ANYWAYS! THE GROUND IS WAY BETTER! COME DOWN AND FIGHT LIKE A MAN!
